sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:modificationsToBackbone: The packaging/helper plasmid pDGM6, which includes the serotype 6 capsid reading frame, was generated by amplifying the capsid genefrom a clone of AAV serotype 6 by PCR using the oligonucleotide primers 5′- ATTTAAATCAGGTATGGCTGCCGATGGT-3′ and 5′- ATCGATTGCTATGGTGACCAGATAAGATAA-3′ encoding terminal SwaI and ClaI restriction sites and inserting the resulting DNA fragment into plasmid pDG cut with the same enzymes.
